content: I live in 12345 zip code. I'm open to trying different types of gyms, but I'd prefer something with a mix of cardio and weightlifting equipment. Budget-friendly options are preferred, and it'd be great if they have group classes too. Oh, and by the way, I've been getting used to my new commute to work, which is about 45 minutes by bus. It's been an adjustment since I used to drive an hour to work every day.
